title: A Review of the UHANS U300 – 5.5″ FHD, MT6750T, 4GB RAM, 4750 mAh for ~$200
text: Looking for a cheap, yet powerful smartphone? Check out XDA Recognized Developer Alberto96 ‘s review of the UHANS U300. It features a 5.5″ 1080p display, a MediaTek MT6750T, 4GB RAM, 32GB internal storage, and a 4,750 mAh battery. For the full list of specifications and an extensive, in-depth review of the device that meets the XDA standard, check out the forum link!
